Aisha Sekindi (amụrụ na 4 Disemba 1970) bụ onye nkuzi na onye omeiwu nke Uganda. Ka ọ na-erule n'ọnwa Febụwarị afọ 2022, ọ na-eje ozi dị ka Minista nke Mmiri nke Uganda na onye nnọchi anya nwanyị maka mpaghara Kalungu na ndị omeiwu nke iri na otu nke Uganda. O nwere otu ọkwa ahụ na omeiwu nke iri nke Uganda
Na ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị, ọ na-esonyere National Resistance Movement n'okpuru tiketi ya ọ gbara ọsọ na ntuli aka nke afọ pụkụ abụọ na iri na isii , merie Aisha Naluyati Waligo.
Aisha Sekindi gara ụlọ akwụkwọ praịmarị nke ndị Alakụba nke ọ hapụrụ na 1984 iji sonye na ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị nke Kadugala maka O Levels (Uganda Certificate of Education), nke ọ nwetara na 1988
Ka e mesịrị na 1995, ọ nwetara asambodo ndị nkuzi na Kibuli Teacher Training College.

Ọ bụ ezie na Aisha Sekindi malitere dị ka osote onye isi ụlọ akwụkwọ na Saint Kizito Primary School, Lwengo (1997 ruo 2001), ọ gara n'ihu ịghọ onye ndụmọdụ mpaghara V nke Lwabenge na odeakwụkwọ maka okike na Gọọmentị Obodo Masaka n'etiti afọ 2001 na 2007.
Tupu ọ bụrụ onye omeiwu, Aisha Sekindi jere ozi dị ka osote Resident District Commissioner maka mpaghara Lira n'etiti afọ 2013 na 2014

Tupu nke ahụ, ọ rụrụ ọrụ n'otu ọkwa ahụ na Tororo District (2011 ruo 2013) na Kamuli District (2007 ruo 2011). N'agbata afọ 2010 na afọ 2011, ọ bụ onye na-anọchite anya Kọmishọna Mpaghara nke Buyende.
